ef=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/portugal-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">3-week Portugal route<\/a> covers a bit of everything! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"monsanto beautiful village portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"monsanto beautiful village portugal\" class=\"wp-image-48655 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105012\/monsanto-beautiful-village-portugal-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01