altinourhair.com\/portugal\/portugal-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">road trip in Portugal<\/a>. So it&#x2019;s best to avoid as many as possible and you may discover some beautiful spots that weren&#x2019;t on your original itinerary, even if it does take a little longer. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To opt for the scenic route, just click the avoid tolls check button on Google Maps.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-1080x767.jpg\" alt=\"travel portugal campervan route\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"320\" alt=\"travel portugal campervan route\" class=\"wp-image-50340 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-1080x767.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-300x213.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-600x426.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-800x568.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-450x320.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-1536x1091.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-portugal-campervan-route-163x116.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104113\/travel-por