18; also shows places to park up for the night, reviewed by other motorhome users.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"campsite campervan portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"campsite campervan portugal\" class=\"wp-image-50466 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104058\/campsite-campervan-portugal-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo