ugaleasycamp.com\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">&#x2018;Portugal Easy Camp&#x2019;<\/a>, where you can camp on remote vineyards and farms, soaking up the wild nature of Portugal. All you have to do in return is purchase the farmer&#x2019;s product\/service.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Our favorite spots during our campervan trip through Portugal:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/GGZAmwXxtEdgP1hK8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Quinta do Pomarinho<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/g.page\/salemaecocamp?share\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Salema Eco Camp<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/KhPj4FgKEQRHgoyv8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Parque de campismo da Praia da Vagueira<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/ZW5Gu6XZcJxt1UR78\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Quinta do Monte Travesso<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104241\/portugal-getting-around-1046x810.jpg\" alt=\"portugal getting around\"><\/noscript><img width=\"436\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal getting around\" class=\"wp-image-50055 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1046px) 100vw, 1046px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104241\/portugal-getting-around-1046x810.jpg 1046w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104241\/portugal-getting-around-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104241\/portugal-getting-around-600x465.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104241\/portugal-getting-around-775x600.jpg 775w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/0