ing through Portugal by campervan is an amazing experience and super easy! Use these tips to make the journey even smoother.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-food-and-water\"><strong>Food and Water<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are plenty of big supermarkets to shop from throughout Portugal, such as Intermache and Lidl. Lidl is particularly cheap to shop for food and can be found in small towns, cities, and on the edge of motorways.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1080x764.jpg\" alt=\"campervan portugal road trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"319\" alt=\"campervan portugal road trip\" class=\"wp-image-50343 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1080x764.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-600x425.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-800x566.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-450x319.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1536x1087.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-163x115.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-254x180.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-768x544.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1024x725.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1440x1019.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104105\/campervan-portugal-road-trip-1080x764.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the campervan you won&#x2019;t have an oven, only a stove, so make sure to take that into account when shopping. Tinned food, pasta, fresh veggies, and fruit are easy to get at all supermarkets.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Although restaurants and cafes will always bring you bottled water, tap water is safe to drink in Portugal. The taste might be not exactly what you&#x2019;re used to, but if you&#x2019;re worried consider using a water purifier. Bring refillable water bottles with you to save on plastic and keep your water cold while traveling. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Here are:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Easy Tips to Travel Plastic-free<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food.jpg\" alt=\"travel portugal campervan food\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel portugal campervan food\" class=\"wp-image-50339 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/23104116\/travel-portugal-campervan-food-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upl